@node sinn "Overview"

Overview:

This program is like Mega/Note (found in Aminet). My program uses MUI.
You can enter some text and it saves it to a file.

@endnode
@node install "Installation"

Installation:

Copy the binary wherever you want.


A data file will be created in the same path.

@endnode
@node bedienung "Usage"

Usage:

Enter text. Quit program.

If you load the program next time, text is still there.


Clipboard functions (cut/copy/paste) are working. You can also print the text.

@endnode
